  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Letter to the health and care sector: preparations for a potential no-deal Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The Secretary of State for Health and Social Care has written to health and care providers about the government's preparations for a potential no-deal Brexit.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

